Hardingin the synchro event last week, was looking to claim his fifth Olympic medal, which would have seen him draw level with Tom Daley as the most successful British diver of all-time.\", \"from\": 407, \"to\": 638, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 579, \"end\": 588, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Daley\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.7099973126800177e-51, \"text\": \"Tom Daley\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Daley\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Daley\"}, {\"begin\": 612, \"end\": 619, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9609080365636085, \"rank\": 0.02120948400844504, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Laugher\", \"from\": 407, \"to\": 414}, {\"ngram\": \"bronze\", \"from\": 427, \"to\": 433}, {\"ngram\": \"Anthony Hardingin\", \"from\": 444, \"to\": 461}, {\"ngram\": \"the synchro event\", \"from\": 462, \"to\": 479}, {\"ngram\": \"his fifth Olympic medal\", \"from\": 512, \"to\": 535}, {\"ngram\": \"level\", \"from\": 568, \"to\": 573}, {\"ngram\": \"all-time\", \"from\": 629, \"to\": 637}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Those hopes were dashed, though, when a poor third dive scored just 35.70, Laugher's total of 410.95 some way short of the 467.05 he had posted in Wednesday's semi-final to qualify for the final ranked third.\", \"from\": 640, \"to\": 848, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Those hopes\", \"from\": 640, \"to\": 651}, {\"ngram\": \"a poor third dive\", \"from\": 678, \"to\": 695}, {\"ngram\": \"Laugher's total\", \"from\": 715, \"to\": 730}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was good enough only for seventh as Chinese pair Xie Siyi and Wang Zongyuan took gold and silver, respectively, to continue their country's dominance of the board at these Games, while Mexico's Osmar Olvera grabbed his second medal of the meet with a phenomenal 500.40 for bronze.\", \"from\": 850, \"to\": 1133, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 889, \"end\": 896, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\", \"score\": 0.9377738560902842, \"rank\": 0.05718761392671335, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\"}, {\"begin\": 902, \"end\": 910, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Xie_Siyi\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Xie Siyi\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Xie_Siyi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Xie_Siyi\"}, {\"begin\": 915, \"end\": 928, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wang_Zongyuan\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Wang Zongyuan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wang_Zongyuan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wang_Zongyuan\"}, {\"begin\": 1038, \"end\": 1044, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mexico_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999760047717595, \"rank\": 2.3965613426196393e-05, \"text\": \"Mexico\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mexico_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mexico_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1047, \"end\": 1052, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Osmar_(footballer,_born_1988)\", \"score\": 0.6438963487818352, \"rank\": 0.35555555555554375, \"text\": \"Osmar\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Osmar_(footballer,_born_1988)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Osmar_(footballer,_born_1988)\"}, {\"begin\": 1053, \"end\": 1059, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olvera\", \"score\": 0.696063440712367, \"rank\": 0.436650657842