ming into this what I could do.\", \"from\": 1282, \"to\": 1323, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In the preliminary rounds and the semi-final, I was taking it as it comes and focusing on myself.\", \"from\": 1324, \"to\": 1421, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the preliminary rounds\", \"from\": 1327, \"to\": 1349}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think here, I let the emotion get the better of me.\", \"from\": 1423, \"to\": 1477, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the emotion\", \"from\": 1444, \"to\": 1455}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I think I wanted the end result too much.\", \"from\": 1478, \"to\": 1519, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 1495, \"to\": 1502}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I thought about that too much over the process.\\\"\", \"from\": 1520, \"to\": 1568, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the process\", \"from\": 1555, \"to\": 1566}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Aquatics GB 'immensely disappointed' as Proud joins Enhanced Games Sports quiz of 2024: 100 hard questions on an incredible year Keely Hodgkinson reveals Grand Slam Track decision and 2025 ambitions The best destinations and activities to book this winter The Chinese duo were always likely to have gold and silver between them, leaving Laugher as favourite for bronze alongside Olvera, one half of the Mexican pair that had come so close to a major upset when winning silver in the synchro event.\", \"from\": 1570, \"to\": 2071, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1701, \"end\": 1717, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keely_Hodgkinson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Keely Hodgkinson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keely_Hodgkinson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keely_Hodgkinson\"}, {\"begin\": 1834, \"end\": 1841, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\", \"score\": 0.9377738560902842, \"rank\": 0.057