//dbpedia.org/resource/Olvera\", \"score\": 0.696063440712367, \"rank\": 0.4366506578421793, \"text\": \"Olvera\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olvera\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olvera\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the pair\", \"from\": 2096, \"to\": 2104}, {\"ngram\": \"his slight miss\", \"from\": 2110, \"to\": 2125}, {\"ngram\": \"a third dive\", \"from\": 2129, \"to\": 2141}, {\"ngram\": \"the door\", \"from\": 2173, \"to\": 2181}, {\"ngram\": \"the Brit\", \"from\": 2186, \"to\": 2194}, {\"ngram\": \"the initiative\", \"from\": 2204, \"to\": 2218}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Instead, though, Laugher over-rotated on his inward three-and-a-half somersaults - on paper one of his two easiest dives - and hit the water hard.\", \"from\": 2221, \"to\": 2367, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Laugher\", \"from\": 2238, \"to\": 2245}, {\"ngram\": \"his inward three-and-a-half somersaults\", \"from\": 2262, \"to\": 2301}, {\"ngram\": \"paper\", \"from\": 2307, \"to\": 2312}, {\"ngram\": \"his two easiest dives\", \"from\": 2320, \"to\": 2341}, {\"ngram\": \"the water\", \"from\": 2352, \"to\": 2361}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It was the nail in the coffin moment at that point, really,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 2369, \"to\": 2439, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the nail\", \"from\": 2377, \"to\": 2385}, {\"ngram\": \"the coffin moment\", \"from\": 2389, \"to\": 2406}, {\"ngram\": \"that point\", \"from\": 2410, \"to\": 2420}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I wished at that point I could have pulled out but I am really happy I continued on.\", \"from\": 2440, \"to\": 2525, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that point\", \"from\": 2453, \"to\": 2463}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am a fantastic athlete and I will always see things through, it just wasn't the fairytale that I wanted it to be.\\\"\", \"from\": 2527, \"to\": 2644, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a fantastic athlete\", \"from\": 2533, \"to\": 2552}, {\"ngram\": \"things\", \"from\": 2575, \"to\": 2581}, {\"ngram\": \"the fairytale\", \"from\": 2606, \"to\": 2619}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The blunder left the 29-year-old almost 40 points adrift of the medals at the halfway stage.\", \"from\": 2646, \"to\": 2738, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The blunder\", \"from\": 2646, \"to\": 2657}, {\"ngram\": \"the 29-year-old almost 40 points\", \"from\": 2663, \"to\": 2695}, {\"ngram\": \"the medals\", \"from\": 2706, \"to\": 2716}, {\"ngram\": \"the halfway stage\", \"from\": 2720, \"to\": 2737}]}, {\"sentence\": \"From there, he needed snookers, but any slim chance of bridging the gap disappeared when Olvera nailed his penultimate dive, a score of 98.80 the highest of any competitor all day and all but securing a medal.\", \"from\": 2739, \"to\": 2948, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2828, \"end\": 2834, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olvera\", \"score\": 0.696063440712367, \"rank\": 0.4366506578421793, \"text\": \"Olvera\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olvera\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olvera\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"snookers\", \"from\": 2761, \"to\": 2769}, {\"ngram\": \"any slim chance\", \"from\": 2775, \"to\": 2790}, {\"ngram\": \"the gap\", \"from\": 2803, \"to\": 2810}, {\"ngram\": \"his penultimate dive\", \"from\": 2842, \"to\": 2862}, {\"ngram\": \"a score\", \"from\": 2864, \"to\": 2871}, {\"ngram\": \"any competitor\", \"from\": 2896, \"to\": 2910}, {\"ngram\": \"a medal\", \"from\": 2940, \"to\": 2947}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Laugher is now 29 and while he has no plans to retire, he admits he does not know whether he will make it to a fifth Games in Los Angeles in four years' time.\", \"from\": 2950, \"to\": 3108, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3076, \"end\": 3087, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.9999999995488906, \"rank\": 3.248039610